Package: BankEfficiencyNDEA
Type: Research
Title: Technical Efficiency of Albanian Banks via Dynamic Network DEA (2021-2023)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Aristea", "Gjokthomi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Dynamic Network Data Envelopment Analysis of nine Albanian banks
    covering 2021-2023. Implements a two-stage production process with
    carry-over effects, bootstrap confidence intervals (Simar & Wilson),
    Malmquist productivity index, and sensitivity analysis on carry-over
    parameters. Includes an interactive Shiny dashboard and a Quarto report.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
